==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Neologize
<hw>Ne*ol"o*gize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
introduce or use new words or terms or new uses of old words.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To introduce innovations in doctrine, esp. in
theological doctrine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Neology</ent>⟦br⟧
